Image Augmentation with The Albumentations Package

Installation

1. Set Up the Virtual Environment: Create and activate a dedicated virtual environment:

conda create -n album python=3.11
conda activate album

2. Install Packages: Install some required packages and the Albumentations package,

conda install opencv
conda install matplotlib
conda install conda-forge::albumentations
conda install notebook

3. Create a Working Directory and cd into it

mkdir augmentation
cd <path/to>/augmentation

4. Download CVA_image_augmentation.ipynb and all the image assets to your working directory.

5. Start Jupyter Notebook and Open CVA_image_augmentation.ipynb

jupyter notebook
